<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<div class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Alan Bishop runs a business advisory company and is a Non-Executive Director/Chairman. Alan Bishop was Chief Executive of the Victorian Chamber of Commerce and Industry for over 5 years, the peak body for business in Victoria.</div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div><div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4ab24e7f" data-id="4ab24e7f" data-element_type="column">
