<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<div class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">JAMES CARL began his long association with the transport industry by purchasing his first truck, a Bedford tray, in the early 1960s. Jame’s love of the industry led him to form Cubico, which was later sold to Mayne Nickless.</div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></section>
